类 ArrayMap<K,​V>

java.lang.Object
java.util.AbstractMap<K,​V>
ArrayMap<K,​V>
类型参数:
K - An eraser element of key will change its format every time the class is reused.
V - An eraser element of value will change its format every time the class is reused. Content:This is a map with generic functions, and its republic is similar to hashmap. He has his own unique set element, and set can print out unique elements. Currently my map does not support remove.
